					<description><![CDATA[<p>Mayo Clinic Healthcare cardiologist shares tips to safely get your blood pumping again LONDON — Around the world, people are starting to engage in outdoor activities after a winter spent largely indoors and perhaps with less physical activity than during more temperate seasons. In other climates, people may be starting an indoor, less-active time. Gosia [&amp;#8230;]</p>
